N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 132.2 - Registration statement

State Regulations

In addition to the information required by General Business

Law, section 369-e(1), the statement filed in the Department of State shall set
forth the prizes offered and the retail value of each prize. Notes
